Because Google is
willing to take

00:05:57.440 --> 00:05:59.230
risks with us, and
willing to experiment,

00:05:59.230 --> 00:06:01.660
and willing to be
innovative, and find

00:06:01.660 --> 00:06:04.460
ways to advance both
of our missions.

00:06:04.460 --> 00:06:07.920
So one thing we've
done together is around

00:06:07.920 --> 00:06:11.300
getting more AP science,
engineering, and math classes

00:06:11.300 --> 00:06:13.760
into under-served communities.

00:06:13.760 --> 00:06:16.640
