incentives in place

00:06:19.150 --> 00:06:21.430
for the teachers
at that school who

00:06:21.430 --> 00:06:23.910
have students that
show potential

00:06:23.910 --> 00:06:26.130
to excel in these areas,
but are essentially

00:06:26.130 --> 00:06:29.070
under-served by the
courses aren't there.

00:06:29.070 --> 00:06:32.650
So we put incentives in
place to start new AP classes

00:06:32.650 --> 00:06:33.370
in those areas.

00:06:33.370 --> 00:06:36.670
Or if there are AP classes,
to add enrollment, and extend

00:06:36.670 --> 00:06:38.400
them, and get resources to them.

00:06:38.400 --> 00:06:40.550
And that's an amazing program.

00:06:40.550 --> 00:06:43.230
We do that with Google, and with
