interested in funding?

00:12:39.250 --> 00:12:42.312
OLIVER HURST-HILLER: Yeah, so
I would say-- one of the things

00:12:42.312 --> 00:12:44.520
that people may not realize
until they visit the site

00:12:44.520 --> 00:12:46.311
