without paper?

00:13:01.049 --> 00:13:03.132
So sometime's it's these
really basic essentials--

00:13:03.132 --> 00:13:05.048
DIANE SOLINGER: We don't
like paper at Google.

00:13:05.048 --> 00:13:07.020
Get the Chrome books.

00:13:07.020 --> 00:13:10.180
OLIVER HURST-HILLER: We have
