value of experimentation.

00:14:08.210 --> 00:14:10.216
So one of these we're
very excited about

00:14:10.216 --> 00:14:12.620
is that many of the
projects are in that area.

00:14:12.620 --> 00:14:15.290
It's not just meeting a need
that should already be met.

00:14:15.290 --> 00:14:19.274
It's helping a teacher be an
innovator on the front liens.

