00:17:54.920 --> 00:17:58.110
They needed a platform first to
really do what I wanted to do.

00:17:58.110 --> 00:18:03.230
And so I've funded projects
with the help of my readers

00:18:03.230 --> 00:18:05.820
for about 200,000
students so far.

00:18:05.820 --> 00:18:09.630
Every year, and just from
a tactical standpoint,

00:18:09.630 --> 00:18:11.430
