00:29:35.480 --> 00:29:38.695
So I think we see it
as a big opportunity.

00:29:38.695 --> 00:29:39.600
And we're fortunate.

00:29:39.600 --> 00:29:43.210
A lot of sites have said, OK,
lots of teachers come here.

00:29:43.210 --> 00:29:44.460
We'll have a network effect.

00:29:44.460 --> 00:29:45.876
And then great
things will happen.

00:29:45.876 --> 00:29:48.400
But they've have a hard
time getting critical mass.

00:29:48.400 --> 00:29:49.844
And we've got the critical mass.

00:29:49.844 --> 00:29:51.635
And I think now challenge
and kind of thing

00:29:51.635 --> 00:29:53.380
we have to brainstorm
with great advisers

00:29:53.380 --> 00:29:55.943
like Time is what do we do
with that now that they're all

00:29:55.943 --> 00:29:56.443
